All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class AppiaInvalidQoSException
extends AppiaException

Thrown when the desired QoS is invalid.
This is normally due to some Event that is required by some Layer, but no other Layer provides it.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Alexandre Pinto
